    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is identical to Hyuuga Ryuu: Hakke Kuushou. If the target hits an object of its own size or larger weighing at least four times as much as it, it suffers 1d4 damage per 10 ft the knockback was cut short.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage and knockback by 1 die, up to 8d6 damage and 5d4 x 5 ft knockback.</p>\n\n",
